<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h1 {
        color: #007bff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .highlight {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #007bff;
      }

      .quote {
        font-style: italic;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to Foodies, where passion for food meets unparalleled dining
        experience. At Foodies, we are dedicated to serving you with the finest
        cuisines crafted by our talented chefs.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our diverse menu offers something for everyone, from classic dishes to
        innovative creations that will ignite your taste buds. Whether you're a
        meat lover, vegetarian, or have special dietary requirements, we have
        options to satisfy your cravings.
      </p>
      <p>
        At Foodies, we believe in creating memories, not just meals. Our warm
        and inviting ambiance coupled with impeccable service ensures that every
        visit is a memorable one. Whether it's a romantic dinner for two, a
        family celebration, or a gathering with friends, we strive to make every
        moment special.
      </p>
      <p class="quote">
        "<span class="highlight"
          >Good food is the foundation of genuine happiness.</span
        >" - <em>Auguste Escoffier</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
